Yep, I find the problem. 
https://github.com/dmlc/mshadow/blob/master/mshadow/tensor_container.h#L174
If this line fails, then the following codes will never be executed. Thus data_.dptr_ will still be NULL when 'delete r' is called.

How about change it to

``` cpp
inline void Release(void) {
  if (data_.dptr_ != NULL) {
    this->shape_[0] = 0;
    this->stride_ = 0;
    this->data_.stride_ = 0;
    this->data_.shape_[0] = 0;
    try {
      mshadow::FreeSpace(&data_);
    } catch (const dmlc::Error &e) {
      this->dptr_ = data_.dptr_ = NULL;
      throw e;
    }
    this->dptr_ = data_.dptr_ = NULL;
  }
}
```
